10-20次或以上至完全聽清楚，並溫習doc入面既vocab<br />\n<a href=\"https://site.douban.com/195274/room/2428543/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsite.douban.com%2F195274%2Froom%2F2428543%2F&d=WzviOvFWrGNRmPFYDsyrJbDFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=7c5466c3\" target=\"_blank\">https://site.douban.com/195274/room/2428543/</a><br />\n<br />\n5. 到3,4 中後期再用iPad 睇幾本外國兒童書打好啲vocab 底同語感(ipad 查解釋快+可以highlight)，因為6000 字真係英文考試既bare minimum，為期1-2個月睇5本書，每日最少40頁，或同等份量報紙<br />\n<br />\n6. 到3,4 中後期每星期兩次逢thur/sun 去cantonese English language exchange meetup 同鬼佬傾計，或搵上網鬼佬傾計都可以，詳情睇meetup 個app 到search，我覺得meetup面對面好啲<br />\n<br />\n1,2 同時做switch 下，得閒要active recall，做exam<br />\n3,4,5 都係要switch 下，得閒要active recall, exam，6 就要長期做，畢竟同鬼佬傾計機會難得<br />\n睇完learning how to learn 你會知點解要咁做<br />\n<br />\n有以上呢最短半年(最好長期做，不過你有其他科）搏命做齊以上既野(係要搏命，無底仲想唔搏命可以返去訓了）打底先開始操dse English 卷，否則你係唔會操到，因為無英文底<br />\n<br />\n有唔明請問，你粗略睇睇3000字入面有幾多個識，識係肯定知解釋先叫識"},{"pid":"e5d78fdbc31f4a75d272e8d08ee6df7f19ed2fe6","tid":965738,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T01:50:11.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"b256812c58d82b201fa5ebebb46bb007144c2722","tid":965738,"uid":171870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T05:01:23.000Z","msg":"其實最好打好個英文底先,如果本身連基本grammar都唔識好難幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0c0cbf923a68987f05d876f8928769889585d12","tid":965738,"uid":171854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b256812c58d82b201fa5ebebb46bb007144c2722","tid":965738,"uid":171870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T05:01:23.000Z","msg":"其實最好打好個英文底先,如果本身連基本grammar都唔識好難幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T08:24:27.000Z","msg":"如果佢廢到咁,自學都晒時間,無得救<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}